    "The main motive of this paper is to precisely detect the EEG signal as to whether normal or seizure-affected by using advanced optimization and classification techniques.",
    "The motivation of this research work is to develop a new and computationally effective disease prediction framework for epileptic seizure detection and classification.",
    "For improving better performance, advanced optimization and classification methodologies are implemented in the proposed framework.",
    "In order to attain better accuracy and performance, the Finite Linear Haar wavelet-based Filtering (FLHF) approach is used for signal preprocessing and normalization.",
    "Then, the Fractional Dimension (FD) based feature extraction is performed to obtain the suitable features from the preprocessed signal."
